These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing, reading, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, comedy, romance, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, climbing, badminton, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, train, roller, car
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
 2. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
 3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
 5. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 8. the person watching action movies is between the person driving the train and the person who's sport is climbing##2
 9. the person driving the car is the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
13. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
14. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person driving the roller##1
15. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person who's sport is climbing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking     | fishing   | rock-climbing | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | action   | thriller   | romance  |
| Sport         | climbing  | badminton  | basketball  | surfing |
| Transport     | scooter    | roller | train     | car    |

