.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, iced-tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: banana, cherry, kiwi, peach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, d&b, jazz, blues
4 different pets are kept: pony, chinchilla, horse, mouse
 1. the fan of jazz is between the owner of the pony and the fan of d&b##2
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
 4. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
 5. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the fan of d&b##8
 6. the person eating peach is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
 8. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of funk is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
11. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the fan of jazz##8
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
14. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
15. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating banana##1
17. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the fan of d&b##8
18. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
19. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | cola | iced-tea | mirinda  | soy-milk  |
| Food          | peach     | cherry | banana | kiwi  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | jazz  | blues | funk |
| Pet           | horse | mouse | pony    | chinchilla  |

