The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, badminton, golf
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 7. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
12. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3

