.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, peach, cauliflower, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, photography, fishing, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, manager, fisherman, librarian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding, sailing, skateboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the photographer##6
 2. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 3. the person eating spinach is the fisherman##1
 4. the person eating peach is between the photographer and the manager##2
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person eating peach##8
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the librarian##1
10. the manager is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the right of the person eating pumpkin##8
12. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
14. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
15. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
