The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, trike, motorbike, helicopter
 1. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 2. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the entrepreneur##8
 3. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
 4. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person driving the motorbike is the colombian##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the brazilian##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is not the turkish##6
 8. the librarian is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 9. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the librarian##3
11. the doctor is on the right of the nurse##1
12. the librarian is not the polish##6
13. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
14. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
15. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the librarian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
