 7. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
10. the engineer is not to the left of the engineer##8
11. the security-guard is on the far left##1
12. the software-developer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the boat is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
14. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
15. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
