.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, d&b, jazz, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, water-polo, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, jet-ski, skateboard
 1. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##8
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan of d&b##8
11. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola   | hot-chocolate     | sprite    | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | classical      | jazz     | d&b     |
| Sport         | badminton | water-polo  | surfing     | parkour  |
| Transport     | helicopter     | jet-ski | skateboard | airplane     |

