.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, milk, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, dancing, writing, cooking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, ambient, blues, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, egyptian, australian, dutch
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the dutch##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of ambient##1
 4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 5. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the left of the fan of rock##8
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the australian##3
 9. the egyptian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
10. the fan of blues is not the japanese##6
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
12. the dutch is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fan of folk is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
14. the japanese is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | lemonade      | iced-tea  | milk | mirinda        |
| Hobby         | cooking | dancing   | gardening   | writing |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | ambient   | blues    | rock      |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | dutch | australian   | japanese    |

