.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, hot-chocolate, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, photographer, software-developer, scientist
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hamster, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, trike, roller, car
 1. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 2. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the photographer##8
 3. the owner of the bird is the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 6. the person driving the car is the person drinking water##1
 7. the scientist is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 8. the software-developer is on the far right##1
 9. the photographer is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
10. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
12. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
13. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the scientist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | water          | lemonade | hot-chocolate        | 7up    |
| Job         | scientist | lawyer   | photographer | software-developer  |
| Pet         | hamster           | bird     | cat       | guinea-pig  |
| Transport   | car            | roller   | trike     | ship |

