.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, hot-chocolate, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing, woodworking, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, doctor, bartender, software-developer
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, scooter, bike
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 2. the security-guard is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person driving the taxi##1
 4. the security-guard is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
 5. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 8. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the bartender##8
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
10. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the software-developer##7
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate        | mirinda        | 7up        | tea   |
| Hobby       | writing      | magic-tricks      | sudoku | woodworking |
| Job         | software-developer | bartender | doctor     | security-guard  |
| Transport   | scooter          | train      | taxi     | bike  |

