.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, cooking, traveling, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, librarian, photographer, electrician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, satire, mystery, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, house, folk, dubstep
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the security-guard##8
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
 4. the electrician is the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the photographer##6
 6. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the fan of house##8
 7. the person watching satire movies is not to the left of the photographer##8
 8. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
 9. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
10. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
11. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the photographer and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | traveling   | dancing   | cooking |
| Job           | security-guard | librarian    | photographer | electrician    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical | satire     | crime    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | folk      | house         | dubstep     |

 